Package: abgeoRdnetenwatchr
Type: Package
Title: Wrapper for the abgeordnetenwatch.de API
Version: 0.1
Authors: Jan Eggers <jan@eggers-elektronik.de>
Maintainer: Jan Eggers <jan@eggers-elektronik.de>
Description: abgeordnetenwatch.de is a public service by an NGO that stores data on political candidates and members of parliament on the regional, national, and European level, as well as parliamentary decisions, committee memberships, and side jobs. This wrapper is intended to make usage of the data and the API easier in R, offering a couple of macros for frequent tasks. 
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: R(>=3.5.2)
Imports:
    jsonlite,
    dplyr,
    stringr,
    lubridate
Suggests:
    testthat
    
